    "descriptionHtml": "<h2>Thirtyfourth</h2>\n<p>New week, new mix. A little birdy from the mountains had to prod me to post this today.</p>\n<p><strong>Monday Music Mix: 34</strong></p>\n<p><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"400\" data-orig-width=\"400\"><img alt=\"image\" src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/b73c1db6dfb13c8fab236ed521780a93/93684f9912d6730d-14/s540x810/6a3caa5cb1fe01397903d11a807718686ea7867c.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"400\" data-orig-width=\"400\"/></figure></p>\n\n<p>Album art featuring work by <a href=\"http://owlandtheanimals.blogspot.com\" target=\"_blank\">Mapache Salado</a></p>\n<p>Tracklist:<br/></p>\n<ol><li>Ha Ha Tonka - Colorful Kids</li>\n<li>Bear Mountain - Congo</li>\n<li><strong>Join the Riot - Queen Marmalade</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Haim - The Wire</strong></li>\n<li>Dum Dum Girls - Mine Tonight</li>\n<li><strong>Pure Bathing Culture - Dream the Dare</strong></li>\n<li>Avec Sans - Hold On</li>\n<li>Cat Power - Cherokee</li>\n<li>Keep Shelly in Athens - Oostende</li>\n<li>Tree - Demons (feat. Beat Culture and Lena Kuhn)</li>\n<li>The Weeknd - Love in the Sky</li>\n<li>Porcelain Raft - The Way Out</li>\n<li>Lolo - Heard it from a Friend</li>\n<li>RJD2 - Her Majesty&rsquo;s Socialist Request</li>\n<li><strong>Happy Hollows - Endless</strong></li>\n</ol><p>* Tracks in bold indicate my favourites</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mega.co.nz/#!Ichl2A5Z!UG--vHXe4-ly4Y4Xo82WbEafgcRx6xquUuZKtdDgOjY\" target=\"_blank\">Download album</a></p>",
